=3D"confluence-anchor-link" id=3D"Requirements5.3-supportedbrowsers"></span=
><span style=3D"color: rgb(79,79,79);">Supported browsers</span></h1>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(79,79,79);">eZ Publish is developed to work pr=
operly and support the following browser configurations for administrator u=
sers:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style=3D"margin-left: 12.0px;"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><s=
pan>Mozilla=C2=AE Firefox=C2=AE, most recent stable version (t</span>ested =
on Firefox&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">29</span><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">)</span></span=
>. eZ&nbsp;<span class=3D"ph">makes every effort to test and support the mo=
st recent version of Firefox.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></p></li>
<li style=3D"margin-left: 12.0px;"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);"><s=
pan>Google Chrome=E2=84=A2, most recent stable version (t</span>ested on ch=
rome&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(51,51,51);">35</span>).<span>&nbsp;Chro=
me applies updates automatically;&nbsp;</span><span class=3D"ph">eZ</span><=
span>&nbsp;makes every effort to test and support the most recent version.<=
/span></span></p></li>
<li style=3D"margin-left: 12.0px;"><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">Mi=
crosoft=C2=AE Internet Explorer=C2=AE versions<span style=3D"color: rgb(51,=
